    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power\nCo. are distributing the poles for\ntheir new line on Addison street\nfrom Liberty to Rowan avenues,\nand actual work on installing the\nline will begin as soon as the frost\nleaves the ground.\n\n\nWork on the new line on North\nDivision street, Liberty to Rowan\navenues, will begin at the same\ntime. These are what is known\nas pioneer\" lines, as they will be\nbuilt into the pines, in a district\nthat Is as yet largely unsettled. 1t\nmeans 10-minute car service or bet\nter for North Division street."
    }
